Author: royalmouse1
Text: I think it's the same with any disorder tbh. Like I can talk about my depression all day but only the pretty parts. Not the "I havent brushed my teeth or showered in 2 weeks" part.  Or "I havent eaten in 3 days" is prettier than "I ate a sleeve of oreos then stuck my fingers down my throat over my toilet"

Author: 3cats_in_atrenchcoat
Text: I feel you on that. I am pretty comfortable talking about My ED in broad strokes with folks I'm close to, but there are certain things I don't think anyone wants to hear about.
